Russia’s Aeroflot Opens Route from Moscow to Croatia’s Dubrovnik

-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 
2011-04-27T14:10:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/russia-s-aeroflot-opens-route-from-moscow-to-croatia-s-dubrovnik.html
Russian national carrier Aeroflot
will introduce a summer route between Moscow and  Croatia ’s
tourist resort town of  Dubrovnik , the Dubrovnik  airport  said
today in a statement on its website.  Flights will be available on Monday, Wednesday and Friday
between June 1 and Sept. 30, it said.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story: Jasmina
Kuzmanovic at   jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story: James M. Gomez
at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  